# Matrix
divide | 
col_shift | Shift all columns of array to the left num_shift times.
row_shift | Shift all rows of array up num_shift times.
ero_replace | From array, add to row1, a multiple of row2.
ero_interchange | Swap row1 and row2 in array.
ero_scaling | Multiply row with multiple in array.
